Last updated: 2 Jan 2013 by Toby Howard

Files in  /opt/info/courses/OpenGL:

Makefile	
	sample Makefile for compiling Mesa programs 
	on School Linux Teaching installation.
	Compiles "thegears.c"

thegears.c
	sample for the aboveMakefile

examples/
	sources of example programs from the COMP27112 OpenGL manual, and also
	some pre-compiled examples from the xscreensaver collection.

tutor/
	OpenGL tutorial programs by Nate Robins. Must be run from the
	tutor/ directory in order to access model data.

Please address queries to toby.howard@machester.ac.uk

[ends]


